{"article_id":"jPzotZqBQL6sG9xF","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Special counsel Robert Mueller ' s 448-page report is a copiously detailed chronicle of shady conduct from Donald Trump and his associates , from the campaign through to the White House .","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"Mueller makes clear","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"that his investigation did not establish","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"that there was a conspiracy between Trump associates and the Russian government","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"to interfere with the election .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"And the special counsel doesn ' t say one way or the other","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"whether he thinks","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"President Trump criminally obstructed justice while in office","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"- though he makes clear","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"he thinks","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"the evidence of that is quite concerning .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"\" If we had confidence after a thorough investigation of the facts","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"that the President clearly did not commit obstruction of justice ,","depth":10},{"id":13,"text":"we would so state , \"","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Mueller writes .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"\" We are unable to reach such a judgment . \"","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"The report makes several things clear :","depth":4},{"id":17,"text":"that the Russian government tried to help Trump win ,","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"that the Trump campaign was eager to benefit from hackings","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"targeting Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"that Trump ' s campaign advisers had a host of ties to Russia ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and that President Trump tried again and again to try to impede the Russia investigation .","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"For instance , Mueller writes","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that Trump \" repeatedly \" asked people","depth":12},{"id":24,"text":"associated with his campaign","depth":12},{"id":25,"text":"to \" find \" tens of thousands of emails","depth":12},{"id":26,"text":"Hillary Clinton had deleted ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"and that campaign adviser Michael Flynn embarked on an","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"( unsuccessful )","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"effort","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"to do so .","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"The special counsel also describes","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"how Trump ' s campaign manager Paul Manafort gave a Russian associate internal polling data","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"and stressed a focus on Midwestern states .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"And the report ' s volume on obstruction of justice lays out facts about Trump ' s behavior on 11 different episodes , from FBI Director James Comey ' s firing to his efforts","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"to intimidate one-time Trump lawyer Michael Cohen .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"Related","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"3 winners and 3 losers from the Mueller report","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"Several loose ends remain .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"A good deal of material in the report is redacted","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"- including ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"it seems ,","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"information about just what exactly happened regarding Roger Stone ' s efforts","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"to get information about hacked emails from WikiLeaks .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Furthermore , an appendix to the report also lays out 14 redacted matters","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"that are still being investigated","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"( two","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that Mueller was handling ,","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"and 12","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"that he referred elsewhere ) .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"But Trump ' s criminal jeopardy from the Mueller probe itself is over .","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"And some Democrats are throwing cold water on any impeachment push","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"based on Mueller ' s findings","depth":7},{"id":53,"text":"-","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"\" based on what we have seen to date ,","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"going forward on impeachment is not worthwhile at this point , \"","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"House Majority Leader Steny Hoyer told CNN Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"Mueller ' s Russian interference findings and his decision","depth":3},{"id":58,"text":"not to charge Trump associates with conspiracy , explained","depth":3},{"id":59,"text":"The first volume of Mueller ' s report focuses on the Russian effort","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"to interfere with the 2016 presidential election ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"and whether any Trump associates were involved in that effort .","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"This is popularly referred to as \" collusion , \"","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"but Mueller writes","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"that collusion is not a criminal term","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"and he instead relied on conspiracy law .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"The volume begins","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"by describing the two major Russian government efforts","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"to interfere with the election .","depth":7},{"id":69,"text":"First , there was the social media propaganda operation","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"- the \" troll farm , \"","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"in which Russia ' s Internet Research Agency","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"( funded by an oligarch","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"known as \" Putin ' s chef \" )","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"created fake online accounts","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"that \" favored candidate Trump","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"and disparaged candidate Clinton , \"","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"according to Mueller .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"The special counsel writes","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"that his investigation has \" not identified evidence","depth":10},{"id":80,"text":"that any Trump Campaign official \" was knowingly involved in their efforts","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"( Mueller indicted several Russian nationals and Russia-affiliated people and organizations in February 2018 ) .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"Second , there was what Mueller calls the \" Russian hacking and dumping operations. \"","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"Russian intelligence officers hacked into the accounts of Clinton campaign and Democratic Party organizations .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Some of that material was then posted online by the Russians themselves ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"while other material was eventually posted by WikiLeaks .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"Mueller does not suggest any involvement from Trump officials in the hacking itself","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"-","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"but his findings about the leaks aren ' t so clear .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"A section","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"titled \" Trump Campaign and the Dissemination of Hacked Materials \"","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"is heavily redacted ,","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"and appears to include information about Trump associates ' discussions about WikiLeaks .","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"( Some of this redacted material likely relates to Trump campaign adviser Roger Stone ,","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"who faces an upcoming trial . )","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"This section also describes how ,","depth":11},{"id":96,"text":"according to Michael Flynn ,","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"Trump repeatedly asked his campaign advisers to find Hillary Clinton ' s deleted emails .","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"( This referred to tens of thousands of emails","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"Clinton deleted","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"rather than hand over to the government , with the justification","depth":13},{"id":101,"text":"that they were personal rather than work-related . )","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"Flynn in fact tried to \" find \" those emails ,","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"contacting an elderly Republican donor","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"who tried to obtain them on the \" dark web. \"","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"He did not succeed .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Beyond probing","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"whether Trump associates were involved in those two main Russian interference operations ,","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Mueller also investigated \" links and contacts \" between Trump associates and people with ties to Russia ' s government .","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"Per Mueller ,","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"the idea was to look into \" whether those contacts constituted a third avenue \" of Russian influence ,","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"and into whether there was a conspiracy","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"involving \" Russia providing assistance to the campaign \" in exchange for future \" favorable treatment . \"","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"This section of the report is more than 100 pages long","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"and explores these , among other , topics :","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"Michael Cohen ' s efforts","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"to advance a project","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"to build a Trump Tower in Moscow ,","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"and outreach to Russian government officials about it","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"George Papadopoulos , a Trump campaign foreign policy adviser , getting a tip","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"that Russia had \" dirt \" on Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"The tip came from a professor with ties to the Russian government .","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"Donald Trump Jr. ' s meeting with a Russian lawyer at Trump Tower in New York ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"to try and get dirt on Hillary Clinton","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"Former Russian ambassador Sergey Kislyak ' s contacts with Trump advisers","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"- including Jeff Sessions , Jared Kushner , and Michael Flynn","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"Paul Manafort ' s longtime Russia and Ukrainian connections , and his contacts with a Russian associate during the campaign ,","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"to whom he provided Trump campaign polling data and talked Midwestern battleground states","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"Trump associate Erik Prince ' s secret meeting in Seychelles with a Russian financier after the election","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"In the end , though , Mueller concluded","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"that none of these contacts added up to \" an agreement","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"to commit any substantive violation of federal criminal law . \"","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"The special counsel also looked into","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"whether Donald Jr. ' s meeting the Russian lawyer violated campaign finance law , under the theory","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"that it involved a request for a \" thing of value \" from a foreigner","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"who ' s not permitted to donate to a US political campaign .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"But Mueller concluded","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"that the evidence","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"he had ,","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"particularly regarding the parties ' intent","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"to violate the law ,","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"wasn ' t sufficient for a likely criminal conviction .","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"An important caveat","depth":11},{"id":143,"text":"Mueller makes","depth":11},{"id":144,"text":"is that","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"when he writes","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"that his investigation \" did not establish particular facts , \"","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"that \" does not mean","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"that there was no evidence of those facts. \"","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"But in the end , his 22-month investigation spent a great deal of time and resources","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"probing these matters","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"- and","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"despite all of the shady information","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"they turned up ,","depth":12},{"id":154,"text":"they didn ' t end up clearly documenting a Trump-Russia election interference conspiracy .","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"The second volume of Mueller ' s report is a detailed investigation of events","depth":8},{"id":156,"text":"that potentially implicate President Trump in obstruction of justice .","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"The special counsel writes","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"that he \" determined not to make a traditional prosecutorial judgment \"","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"on whether Trump committed criminal obstruction of justice .","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"The main reason","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"he did so","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"was because the Justice Department has held","depth":12},{"id":163,"text":"that a sitting president can ' t be indicted .","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"\" We determined not to apply an approach","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"that could potentially result in a judgment","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"that the President committed crimes , \"","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"he writes .","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"Oddly , though , Mueller also goes out of his way to point out","depth":11},{"id":169,"text":"that he does not have \" confidence \"","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"that Trump did not obstruct justice","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"- and claims","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"that ,","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"if Trump indeed \" clearly did not commit obstruction of justice , \"","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"he would say so .","depth":13},{"id":175,"text":"The implication is that the evidence against Trump on obstruction shouldn ' t be dismissed lightly","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"( even though Attorney General Bill Barr did end dismissing it rather lightly ) .","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"The key obstruction-related events","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"Mueller collected facts and evidence on","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"are :","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"Trump insisted","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"that he doubted","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"that Russia was behind the hacking of Democrats ' emails ,","depth":12},{"id":183,"text":"and denied having any business in Russia","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"even though his company was trying to build a skyscraper in Moscow .","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"Trump tried to get FBI Director James Comey to drop an investigation into Michael Flynn","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"( but Comey didn ' t do it ) .","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"Trump tried several times to get Attorney General Jeff Sessions to reverse his recusal from oversight of the Russia investigation","depth":13},{"id":188,"text":"or to rein in the probe .","depth":13},{"id":189,"text":"Trump fired Comey .","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"Trump directed McGahn to have Mueller himself fired","depth":13},{"id":191,"text":"( but McGahn didn ' t carry this out ) .","depth":13},{"id":192,"text":"Trump tried to prevent the disclosure of emails","depth":14},{"id":193,"text":"revealing Donald Jr. ' s meeting at Trump Tower with a Russian lawyer .","depth":14},{"id":194,"text":"Trump and his legal team urged key figures in the probe","depth":16},{"id":195,"text":"( like Paul Manafort )","depth":16},{"id":196,"text":"not to \" flip \"","depth":15},{"id":197,"text":"and attacked those","depth":15},{"id":198,"text":"who did flip","depth":16},{"id":199,"text":"( like Michael Cohen ) .","depth":16},{"id":200,"text":"Much of this seems to be clearly aimed at trying to impede the Russia investigation .","depth":8},{"id":201,"text":"And some of the details here are very juicy indeed .","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"For instance , an administration official ' s notes describe Trump ' s reaction","depth":13},{"id":203,"text":"upon learning of Mueller ' s appointment :","depth":13},{"id":204,"text":"\" Oh my God .","depth":14},{"id":205,"text":"This is terrible .","depth":14},{"id":206,"text":"This is the end of my Presidency .","depth":14},{"id":207,"text":"I ' m fucked. \"","depth":14},{"id":208,"text":"After that , Trump spoke to his advisers","depth":13},{"id":209,"text":"about \" knocking out Mueller \"","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"and tried","depth":14},{"id":211,"text":"- unsuccessfully -","depth":14},{"id":212,"text":"to have Jeff Sessions rein in the Russia investigation .","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"We also learned","depth":12},{"id":214,"text":"that ,","depth":13},{"id":215,"text":"when Flynn moved toward cooperating with the government ,","depth":14},{"id":216,"text":"Trump ' s lawyer told Flynn ' s attorney","depth":15},{"id":217,"text":"that he interpreted this as an expression of hostility toward the president","depth":16},{"id":218,"text":"and that he planned to make Trump aware of it .","depth":16},{"id":219,"text":"And that","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"after Paul Manafort and Rick Gates were indicted ,","depth":13},{"id":221,"text":"Manafort told Gates","depth":14},{"id":222,"text":"that it would be stupid to strike a plea deal ,","depth":15},{"id":223,"text":"since Trump ' s lawyer had made clear","depth":16},{"id":224,"text":"they ' d \" be taken care of . \"","depth":16},{"id":225,"text":"Mueller writes","depth":8},{"id":226,"text":"that the evidence doesn ' t establish","depth":10},{"id":227,"text":"that all this \" was designed to cover up a conspiracy between the Trump campaign and Russia \" -","depth":10},{"id":228,"text":"but that Trump could well have had other corrupt motives .","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"For instance ,","depth":9},{"id":230,"text":"regarding Trump ' s firing of Comey ,","depth":10},{"id":231,"text":"Mueller writes :","depth":10},{"id":232,"text":"\" The president had a motive","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"to put the FBI ' s Russia investigation behind him ...","depth":10},{"id":234,"text":"a thorough FBI investigation would uncover facts about the campaign and the President personally","depth":10},{"id":235,"text":"that the President could have understood to be crimes","depth":11},{"id":236,"text":"or that would give rise to personal and political concerns . \"","depth":11},{"id":237,"text":"For many of these potentially obstructive incidents , Mueller includes some analysis","depth":9},{"id":238,"text":"of what the evidence shows about the three requirements","depth":11},{"id":239,"text":"for whether something can be considered criminal obstruction of justice","depth":11},{"id":240,"text":"- whether it involves an obstructive act ,","depth":11},{"id":241,"text":"whether it has a connection to a pending proceeding ,","depth":12},{"id":242,"text":"and what Trump ' s intent was .","depth":12},{"id":243,"text":"But , throughout , Mueller avoids coming to a conclusion","depth":9},{"id":244,"text":"on whether any of these individual acts","depth":11},{"id":245,"text":"- or the combination of them -","depth":11},{"id":246,"text":"qualify as criminal obstruction of justice .","depth":10},{"id":247,"text":"He does , however , occasionally to allude","depth":9},{"id":248,"text":"that another federal government body can address the matter :","depth":9},{"id":249,"text":"\" We concluded","depth":10},{"id":250,"text":"that Congress has authority","depth":12},{"id":251,"text":"to prohibit a President ' s corrupt use of his authority","depth":12},{"id":252,"text":"in order to protect the integrity of the administration of justice . \"","depth":11},{"id":253,"text":"And toward the end of the document , the special counsel writes :","depth":10},{"id":254,"text":"\" The protection of the criminal justice system from corrupt acts by any person","depth":12},{"id":255,"text":"- including the President -","depth":12},{"id":256,"text":"accords with the fundamental principle of our government","depth":12},{"id":257,"text":"that ' [ n ] o [ person ] in this country is so high","depth":13},{"id":258,"text":"that he is above the law . ' \"","depth":13}],"relations":[{"parent":517,"left":315,"right":516,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":315,"left":294,"right":314,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":294,"left":274,"right":293,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":0,"right":273,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":262,"right":272,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":262,"left":1,"right":261,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":261,"left":2,"right":260,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":260,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":267,"right":271,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":264,"right":266,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":5,"right":263,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":263,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":266,"left":8,"right":265,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":265,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":271,"left":270,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":270,"left":269,"right":14,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":268,"right":13,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":268,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":293,"left":16,"right":292,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":292,"left":17,"right":291,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":291,"left":289,"right":290,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":289,"left":286,"right":288,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":286,"left":277,"right":285,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":275,"right":276,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":275,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":276,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":285,"left":22,"right":284,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":284,"left":280,"right":283,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":278,"right":279,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":278,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":25,"right":26,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":281,"right":282,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":281,"left":27,"right":28,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":282,"left":29,"right":30,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":288,"left":31,"right":287,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":287,"left":32,"right":33,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":290,"left":34,"right":35,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":314,"left":295,"right":313,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":295,"left":36,"right":37,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":313,"left":306,"right":312,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":306,"left":38,"right":305,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":305,"left":299,"right":304,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":299,"left":39,"right":298,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":296,"right":297,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":296,"left":40,"right":41,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":297,"left":42,"right":43,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":304,"left":300,"right":303,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":300,"left":44,"right":45,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":303,"left":301,"right":302,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":301,"left":46,"right":47,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":302,"left":48,"right":49,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":